"Very sorry that I can't come just between half-past six and nine," she said with a faint smile.
"The princess will be very sorry."
"And so am I."
"You're going, no doubt, to hear Patti?"
said Tushkevitch.
"Patti?
You suggest the idea to me.
I would go if it were possible to get a box."
